➜动态丨南京市栖霞区八卦洲幼儿园：大班远足活动
http://www.sohu.com/a/430862490_100262774	27183
<p>为了增强幼儿体质，培养幼儿吃苦耐劳的精神。11月10日，<strong>南京市栖霞区八卦洲幼儿园</strong>在陌上花渡组织大班进行<strong>远足活动</strong>。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=223152648&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201110/d5989dbc4f0a42f98d4396661b6c7883.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201110/289b8337d2954cb696d7b7e40405d94f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>柳迎堤转，波随风急。秋季的陌上花渡处处充满田园风光。</strong>上午，幼儿们在风景如画的陌上花渡门口集合，通过各班教师和家长志愿者的带领分别沿路线参观与自己班级班本课程相关的场馆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201110/c8de1805aba24e5fa03c505b02510871.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
